b'Follow Max and his brother Matthias, both technical students at @siemens_ausbildung, on their journey to the #allianzarena. They will find out how we help our partner @fcbayern to always ensure perfect conditions for the players and fans and how we support them in shaping their infrastructural future through digital transformation. And they will also meet a special guest. :winking_face:\n\xe2\x80\xa2\n#realizedigitaltransformation #fcbayernmu\xcc\x88nchen'

b'The edition of the Siemens Ingenious Award ended on a high note, at the Pompidou Centre. The 3 finalists: Marie (@marie.lelouche) , Olivier (@o.bemer) and Salome\xcc\x81 (@salomechatriot), the winner, presented their works to the jury members. For Salome\xcc\x81, the adventure will continue\xe2\x80\xa6 
To find out more: sie.ag/2ICVMOH
 
#Innovation #Digitalisation #ArtCreation'

b'The #SiemensIngeniousAward for Digital Art has sprung from the notion that the worlds of leading-edge industry and contemporary art share the same technological expressive landscape. This award will go to one of 11 young French artists who is able to demonstrate originality, digital creativity, and find extraordinary ways of incorporating digital technologies into the creative process. Award ceremony on October 28, 2020, in Paris.
Check out our IGTV series to stay up to date. 
 
#Innovation #Digitalisation #ArtCreation'

b'A smart Brazilian city! #Aguaduna is the first project in the world that implements an innovative city model, dedicated to recovering the balance between society and nature in the search for the best quality of life for its inhabitants. Located in the municipality of #EntreRios, on the northern coast of the #Bahia state, the binational project soon will be under construction.\n.\n#smartcities #smartcity #urbanspaces #Brazil #smarttech #SiemensBrasil #ciudadinteligente'

b'\xe2\x80\x9eI\xe2\x80\x98m proud to work for Siemens and I\xe2\x80\x98m proud of being an essential worker.\xe2\x80\x9c
Monica, who works at @siemens_mobility, shares how everyday life and work changed for her and her family due to COVID-19.
.
#NewNormal #covid19 #OurWayForward #siemens #newnormallife #togetherwearestronger'

b'Did you know? 20% of global CO2 emissions come from #industrialmotors. Newest norms in the EU will save 40 million tons of CO2/y. #SIMOTICS is leading the race to #ultralowenergy and already fulfils these regulations.\n#beautyofmotors\n#passionformotors'

b'Having drinking water out of the tap is taken for granted in many parts of the :globe_showing_Americas:. The truth is that even in :sweat_droplets:-rich countries, securing water supply is a complex task.
Join our virtual Water Expo
:backhand_index_pointing_right: sie.ag/waterexpo :backhand_index_pointing_left:
and learn how digitalization and innovative technologies like AI can ensure greater security of supply in the water industry. :droplet:by :droplet:
.
#drinkingwater #water #cleanwater #watertreatment #purewater #waterislife #drinkwater #safewater #potablewater #waterquality #wastewater #reverseosmosis #artificialintelligence #ai #technology #automation #digitaltransformation'

b'Every difficult situation is an opportunity to grow and #learnfromit. :light_bulb:
Working from home for months during the pandemic certainly taught us a lot (and still does!). :adult:\xe2\x80\x8d:laptop_computer:

What has changed for you and what did you learn from it? :sparkles:

b'Did you know? 70% of electricity consumption in EU industry is from #industrialmotors. New #Ecodesign norms will save 110TWh by 2030 (\xe2\x89\x88 consumption of Netherlands). #SIMOTICS is leading in #ultralowenergy :star-struck: #beautyofmotors\n#passionformotors'

b'Did you know? There are 8 billion #industrialmotors in the EU. #EnergyEfficiency is key in #SIMOTICS which achieves IE3 #Ecodesign standards coming in 2021 and some even IE4 standards. Time to switch! #beautyofmotors #ultralowenergy'

b'We are very happy that our long-time partner @salzburgerfestspiele has found a safe way to host the festival this year in spite of all the difficulties. :party_popper: \nThis year has proven to be a great challenge for cultural institutions but that made us realize once more what an important part of our community and cultural identity they are. This first episode of #housesofsmart was recorded last year and shows how we get involved as partners and what role we play in this event by providing smart infrastructure solutions and offering spaces of encounter for cultural exchange and interaction. #siemensculture'

b'Did you know? #electricmotors use 50% of EU electricity. If not for the exceptional #EnergyEfficiency of #SIMOTICS, this would be more. They already beat future #Ecodesign regulations. Time to switch. https://sie.ag/3jAnVE4\n#beautyofmotors #ultralowenergy'

b'In 1929, we electrified a whole country by using the power of water.\xc2\xa0:high_voltage:\xc2\xa0Did you know that Siemens built a huge hydroelectric power plant at the River Shannon in Ireland? Swipe through our great historic pictures and get a glimpse at the impressive size of the project\xc2\xa0:eyes:\n\n#siemenshistory'

b'Thanks #SINUMERIK for being our #BFF for 6 decades. :party_popper: We\xe2\x80\x99re good #industrialmotors. But with you, we\xe2\x80\x99re great. Looking forward to the next 60. #SIMOTICS #SINUMERIK #bettertogether #beautyofmotors #passionformotors'

b'To keep a metro system running :tram:on time and efficiently, you need a reliable supply of #energy :high_voltage:. Together with @ColasRail_off , we\xe2\x80\x99ll enhance the #commute times & increase the comfort for millions of Egyptians in #Cairo :family_man_woman_girl_boy: https://sie.ag/2XrSqD7'

b'While we adapt to this new normal, it\xe2\x80\x99s still important to believe in one another and the warm resilience of the human spirit. By standing united, we can shine a light during these uncertain times. Let us show the world that we will persevere, as we are #InThisTogether.'

b'Today is the International Day Against Homophobia, Transphobia and Biphobia. While we should take a stand against these fobias every day, on this day people all over the globe join in to say no :woman_gesturing_NO-dark_skin_tone::man_gesturing_NO_medium_skin_tone::person_gesturing_NO_light_skin_tone: #IDAHOBIT'

b'Wondering what keeps the wheels of industry turning? In the #bread industry, our #SIMOTICS #industrialmotors move grain in silos, drive the mills and help knead and bake loaves. The dust requires them to be explosion-proof to keep the food supply safe.\n#beautyofmotors #passionformotors #electricmotors #ingenuity #technology #industry #Siemens #picoftheday #motors'

b'Do you want to find out more about our #Vectron :mountain_railway:? Follow one of our favorite accounts :right_arrow_selector: @siemens_mobility :partying_face: #vectron1000 #infrastructure #trainspotter #railroad #railstagram'

b'Wondering what keeps the wheels of industry turning? In water, #SIMOTICS motors drive pumps and compressors to help keep the supply going and treat wastewater. Highly reliable and automated, they\xe2\x80\x99re key to infrastructure. .\n#beautyofmotors #passionformotors #wastewater #electricmotors #wastewatertreatment #ingenuity #technology #industry #Siemens #picoftheday #motors #waterislife'
